                    "description": "The default 1 um grassland particle in a weakly turbulent surface layer, u_star = 0.1 m/s (a quarter of the default). Sluggish turbulence raises both r_a and r_b, throttling the resistance-network deposition pathway, so v_d ~ 0.26 mm/s falls below the default case -- approaching the gravitational-settling floor v_s set by Eq. 19.18. The opposite friction-velocity limb to strong_turbulence.",
